ygData.subject: Re: Electrum enchantments
ygData.msgSnippet: your time/money being a waste is true only if every other player on your server feels as you do.  But I don t think this is true and you ll be able to sell
ygData.messageBody:
your time/money being a waste is true only if every other player on your
server feels as you do. But I don't think this is true and you'll be
able to sell whatever magic stuff you make just fine. Abyway, electrum
is just a way to platinum :)

From: Miko, Jeff [mailto:JMiko@...]

Subject: [eqenchanters] Re: Electrum enchantments

I think only getting a +1 or +2 <anything> from using Electrum is a
waste of time. This really disappoints me. I have already sunk 60p in my
jewelcraft skill and if this list is true then I wasted my time and
money.
